{"tid":708644,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【倫常慘劇】阿瑜原是品學兼優中學生 唯入讀中大後2015年突退學","createTime":"2018-06-19T12:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-19T15:14:40.000Z","uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"88ef93f93eb9d73f89b4045d4ba3ebb25671f1e7","tid":708644,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180619/large/1529391222_d8ce.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180619%2Flarge%2F1529391222_d8ce.jpg&h=b2444a09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n阿瑜平日表現樂觀，在中大讀書期間除了參與學生會做幹事，也曾在歌唱比賽中獲冠軍。<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌弒父弒母再自殺的23歲少女阿瑜，自小品學兼優，花名「彭彭(姓氏)」原外向好動，生前與父母及胞姊同住於屯門新屯門中心的兇案現場單位。阿瑜中學時就讀區內Band 1名校保良局百周年李兆忠紀念中學，於5年前的文憑試中更考獲一科5*成績，據悉她最終獲中大取錄修讀與護理相關的學系，並曾入住中大崇基學院的宿舍。但中大發言人指阿瑜2015年1月已離校，即是未能畢業，但發言人未有解釋她離校的理由。<br />\n<br />\n同學又指阿瑜在大學時期仍頗為活躍，除曾擔任宿生會幹事，亦有參加過大學的歌唱比賽獲得冠軍，另她雖然受濕疹困擾致臉部常有紅斑或「粒粒」，但表面看來為人仍然樂觀，亦有參與球類活動。不過阿瑜在網上討論區留言時，卻常顯出她抑鬱的一面，特別是她講述自己濕疹發作時的慘痛經歷，行文間流露出無助無奈的心情。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180619/58336691\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F58336691&d=uQGCxC8pIIPMHKLX8tu5Fp7TfgnX9jywtYe9GXZmhCU%3D&h=30efea7f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180619%2F58336691&h=62217b21\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20180619/58336691</a>"},{"pid":"ebc93ddf813373f08d1f589590592c53a9b84025","tid":708644,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:53:27.000Z","msg":"佢d經歷都幾耐人尋味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14bce96b01b2659e389711470a0fbf03ad9dabb9","tid":708644,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T12:59:56.000Z","msg":"似中二病發作"},{"pid":"bcdf71d3fa1425c51c3b523cf468c690859ba038","tid":708644,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:03:32.000Z","msg":"可能係濕疹發到返唔到學...如果真係就好慘"},{"pid":"1be1ea09f63fa1c26a039e9e5d30e2a1712ecb8e","tid":708644,"uid":49391,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:50:43.000Z","msg":"有無人有陰囊濕疹?<br />\n成日R到個袋損曬,出曬水?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37e439e5526375eb2adb6ad8a6731887fa51eb99","tid":708644,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"幫落又唔似咁嚴重<br />\n係咪近期惡化"},{"pid":"9e0558f678fe00afd7a1eea92b2494fba0b73fb4","tid":708644,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"37e439e5526375eb2adb6ad8a6731887fa51eb99","tid":708644,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"幫落又唔似咁嚴重<br />\n係咪近期惡化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"有好多人有陰囊濕疹你都唔知啦,唔睇條友個春袋你點知?"},{"pid":"4843ce436a26f2d32201f2aeaf9937111f46035e","tid":708644,"uid":29804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:43:49.000Z","msg":"被玩"},{"pid":"86d46d0669fba7d9e31b2b26d97cad1ab1bf3eed","tid":708644,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9e0558f678fe00afd7a1eea92b2494fba0b73fb4","tid":708644,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"37e439e5526375eb2adb6ad8a6731887fa51eb99","tid":708644,"uid":31374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T13:51:46.000Z","msg":"幫落又唔似咁嚴重<br />\n係咪近期惡化"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T14:32:16.000Z","msg":"有好多人有陰囊濕疹你都唔知啦,唔睇條友個春袋你點知?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T15:14:40.000Z","msg":"駁唔到"}]}